docs.lead_paragraph: The social event in Chinatown to-day will be a dinner given by Robert Mitchell Floyd to Prof. Charles G.D. Roberts at the restaurant of Me Hong Low, which is beneath the fashionable Joss house at 14 Mott Street. Tun Farr, who is of B.L. Wing Co., 10 Bowery, is involved in the affair in some curious Oriental way.

headline.main: ELABORATE CHINESE DINNER.; A Feast of Twelve Courses in Honor of Prof. Roberts.
